    },
    {
      "id": "6a60ae4c0000000000d8b974",
      "text": "[【2026年版】GAFAMの次は「MATANA」？エヌビディア含む新・巨大IT企業群を徹底解説 - DXportal https://www.dx-portal.biz/gafam_matana/]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1784720973,
      "updated": 1784720975
    },
    {
      "id": "6a60ae3e0000000000d8b96b",
      "text": "> 「MATANA」とは、米シリコンバレーのテック企業をリサーチするコンステレーション・リサーチ創業者の[レイ・ワン]氏が生み出した造語であり、下記の6社の頭文字を取っています。",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1784720959,
      "updated": 1784720983
    },
    {
      "id": "6a60ae3f0000000000d8b96d",
      "text": ">  [Microsoft]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1784720959,
      "updated": 1784720985
    },
    {
      "id": "6a60ae3f0000000000d8b96e",
      "text": ">  [Amazon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1784720959,
      "updated": 1784720986
    },
    {
      "id": "6a60ae3f0000000000d8b96f",
      "text": ">  [TESLA]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1784720959,
      "updated": 1784720987
    },
    {
      "id": "6a60ae3f0000000000d8b970",
      "text": ">  [Alphabet]（[Google]）",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1784720959,
      "updated": 1784720995
    },
    {
      "id": "6a60ae3f0000000000d8b971",
      "text": ">  [NVIDIA]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1784720959,
      "updated": 1784720992
    },
    {
      "id": "6a60ae3f0000000000d8b972",
      "text": ">  [Apple]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1784720959,
      "updated": 1784720993
    },
    {
      "id": "6a60ae3f0000000000d8b973",
      "text": "> つまり、[GAFAM]からFacebook（Meta社）が脱落し、新たにTESLAとNVIDIAが加わったということです。",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1784720959,
      "updated": 1784720998
    },
